# Cortex MCP — Documentation & Knowledge Base

Cortex is our team's documentation platform (Docmost instance) accessible via MCP tools.

**URL:** https://cortex.misfitsandmachines.com

## Setup

Add to your `~/.cursor/mcp.json`:

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "cortex-production": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": [
        "mcp-remote",
        "https://mcp-server-production-baf7.up.railway.app/mcp/",
        "--header",
        "Authorization:${CORTEX_API_KEY}"
      ],
      "env": {
        "CORTEX_API_KEY": "Bearer <your-api-key>"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

Get your API key at: https://cortex.misfitsandmachines.com/settings/account/api-keys

## Available Tools

### Page Operations

| Tool | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `page_create` | Create a new page |
| `page_read` | Read page content (supports markdown format) |
| `page_list` | List pages in a space |
| `page_delete` | Delete a page |
| `page_move` | Move page in hierarchy |

### Granular Editing

| Tool | Purpose |
