| `page_append` | Add content to end of page |
| `page_insert_at` | Insert content at specific position |
| `page_update_section` | Update a section by heading name |
| `page_replace_blocks` | Replace N blocks with M blocks |
| `page_delete_blocks` | Delete blocks at position |

